  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with NSCLC who undergo radiation as part of a definitive course of treatment will be
      enrolled. Blood collections will be obtained before, during, and after radiotherapy. We will
      collect demographic and treatment data and explore &amp; describe the pattern of CTC detection in
      all patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
