  </study_design_info>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Circulating tumor cells will be detected by imaging for green fluorescent protein (GFP) which measures cells which high levels of telomerase activity after adenovirus transduction. CTCs are measured in units of number of GFP-positive cells /mL.</measure>
    <time_frame>24 months</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
